Description: A letter from the Church of Smyrna to the Church of Philomelium,
  reporting the martyrdom of St Polycarp.
---
We will celebrate the natal day of his martyrdom in joy and gladness, both in
commemoration of those who finished their contest before, and to prepare those
that shall finish hereafter.
